name: Jet Shooter (Flash Gaming)
description:
JET SHOTTER

Jet shooter another is the  2d arcade game is test version launch. Game mechanism is The player would fly a combat jet aircraft in the skies against enemy forces. In game where the player must take down squadrons of alien ships while avoiding their missiles – hits the arcades in Japan. this Shooter game is another similar game of the galaxy shooter.

                                                                    JET SHOOTER CONTROL

1. W,A,S,D- To motion control of plane.

2.Auto Fire - the player plane fire the missile automatically.

3.Spacebar ,Q  - to fire missile to enemy. this feature is coming soon in the android.

                                                         JET SHOOTER SUPPORTED PLATFORM

1.Windows.

2.Android.
